::Striker::

Striker smiles, looking at Spears in his arms. He didn't mind flying her to 
the Ark, in fact he rather enjoyed it. His last doubts about her dissapeared, 
Striker finally deciding that he had been silly to even think that.

He turns slightly, avoiding a tree. They wern't too far from the Ark. Soon, 
they'd get there.
